import { Input,Grid } from "@nextui-org/react"

export const Hero = () => {
    return(
        <Grid.Container gap={4}>
        <Grid xs={12} sm={6} md={6} lg={6}>
          <Svg />
          </Grid>
        
        
        <Grid>
          <Input 
            underlined 
            labelPlaceholder="Success" 
            color="success" 
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Input 
            underlined 
            labelPlaceholder="Warning" 
            color="warning" 
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid>
          <Input 
            underlined 
            labelPlaceholder="Error" 
            color="error" 
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid.Container>
    )
}
